title: "Lula — Production-grade multi-agent coding assistant"
abstract: >
  Lula is a production-ready LangGraph-based multi-agent coding assistant with a
  sandboxed Rust execution engine. It features a 9-node DAG orchestrator, tripartite
  persistent memory, HMAC-SHA256 approval gates, cross-repo SCIP symbol indexing,
  Firecracker MicroVM isolation, and a structured eval framework with SWE-bench support.
version: "1.0.0-rc4"
date-released: "2026-03-20"
license: MIT
